edu.gvsu.kurmasz.zawilinski

Class PageFilterListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.xml.bind.Unmarshaller.Listener
      • edu.gvsu.kurmasz.zawilinski.PageFilterListener

  • public class PageFilterListener
extends Unmarshaller.Listener
    Handles events from unmarshaller. In particular, when a Wiktionary page has finished loading, this code checks to see if the page is wanted. If not, it removes that page, thereby freeing memory.

    Log data for pages: #pages_kept #pages_total title page_size
    Log data for revisions: #revisions_kept_total #revisions_total rev_number rev_size

    Author:
    Zachary Kurmas
